Sc2Hack / AnotherSc2Hack [as of Version 0.2.5.11 and above]
Written and contributed by bellaPatricia
###############################################

- This software is for education purposes ONLY
- You may harm Blizzard Entertainments ToS when using this software
- You or your Battle.Net Account may get banned


FEATURES:
###############################################
- Get Resource [Minerals, Gas, Supply] of all players
- Get Income [Minerals, Gas, Workers] of all players
- Get Apm [Action per Minute AND Effective Action per Minute] of all players
- Get Armysize [Minerals, Gas, Supply] or all players
- Get Workercount [Amount of workers] of yourself
- Get Minimap [Redrawn position of units] of all players
- Get Unit count [Exact amount of units] of all players

- Get A LOT filter options
- Update deamon for the latest updates
- Fully customizable Caller [Hotkeys and Chatinput] to launch and edit the panels
###############################################


